	   <tr><td colspan=2>I think that many share your opinion on not procing much....&nbsp;&nbsp;=)<br><br>It is primarily based on your DEX, which, as an ORG, is one of your drawbacks (you aint nimble as heck).  Probably the best way to have it proc more often is to increase your DEX, but Im not aware of anyone having a lot of luck getting that spell to proc much anyways, so I wouldnt kill myself over it.  At 55, Shroud of Death will proc far more often (&amp; for more points) &amp; you will be a lot more happy assuming that you can play him that far...<br><br>I would assume that a fast weapon will have the chance to proc more often than a slow weapon, but BABS is a decent weapon. so I would only change out if you have a decent piercing weapon. One weapon that you might want to consider is Centi Warspear.  Its really cheap on my server, has a higher DPS and is a faster weapon than BABS.  However, your dmg bonus might go down as a result of the lower delay, but if you are interested in procing (w/o a substantial loss of weapon ability) Centi might be a decent change.  Centi is 2HP by the way.  <br><br>I still recommend MoSS over most other weapons however if you can afford it.  It has a slightly smaller DPS, but you can wield a shield with it.  MoSS is probably a little more expensive though, so take your pick   =P<br><br>Lunatic<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
